paragraphs.title: Countries with total Alerts greater than 10
paragraphs.text:
%mongo

var alerts = db.records.aggregate([
    { $group: { _id:"$Country", totalAlert: { $sum: "$Alert" } } },
    { $match: { totalAlert: { $gt: 10 } } }, 
    { $sort: { totalAlert: 1 } }
    ])
    
print("%table Country\ttotalAlert")
alerts.forEach(a => {print(a._id + "\t" + a.totalAlert)})

paragraphs.title: Distribution of riots by day of week ranging from 1 (for Monday) to 7 (for Sunday)
paragraphs.text:
%mongo

    { $group: { _id: { $isoDayOfWeek: [{$toDate: "$Timestamp"}] }, totalAlert: { $sum: "$Alert" } } },
    { $sort: { totalAlert: -1 } }
    ])
    
print("%table day of week 1 (for Monday) to 7 (for Sunday)\ttotalAlert")
